transcriber (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Offline voice-to-text transcription using Whisper large-v3-turbo model.
  * Bundled turbo model (ggml-large-v3-turbo-q8_0.bin) in package.
  * GTK3-based GUI with system tray support.
  * D-Bus activation for GNOME dock integration.
  * ALSA audio capture.
  * Optional CUDA GPU acceleration.

 -- Piyush Raizada <piyush.raizada@gmail.com>  Mon, 29 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000
